room_title: Escape room "Zombie Breach" by A2Z Escape in Hays
review: We did the Zombie Escape room and loved it! It was so well thought out and a good challenge. We will be back to try other rooms soon!

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Breach" by A2Z Escape in Hays
review: We had a lot of fun in the Zombie room! It was a hard room, with lots to figure out. Unfortunately, we became zombie food. Hope we have better luck next time. Can't wait for the next room!
